text: Davletkulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Korneyevsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 145 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Meleuz, 6 km from Korneyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Davletkulovo
